760
00:46:10,510 --> 00:46:14,178
Yeah, she did
when she was here before too.

761
00:46:24,590 --> 00:46:26,357
(COMMUNICATOR CHIMES)

762
00:46:26,359 --> 00:46:30,327
- MEDORIN:<i> Akae?</i>
- Yes.

763
00:46:31,097 --> 00:46:34,498
<i>We can't help you. I'm sorry.</i>

764
00:46:36,569 --> 00:46:38,769
But... Please.

765
00:46:42,008 --> 00:46:44,208
(CALL DISCONNECTS)

766
00:46:44,977 --> 00:46:47,111
(BANGS COMMUNICATOR ON TABLE)

